STATE
v.
Michael Anthony ELLIOTT. No. 716P05-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 2, 2006. Daniel P. O'Brien, Assistant Attorney General, Michael Nifong, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 16th day of February 2006 by Defendant for Objections to the Recommendations of the Magistrate Judge:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 2nd day of March 2006."
